2.4.2 The Scope Plane
---------------------

On the functionality side, the strategy is translated into scope through
the creation of *functional specifications*: a detailed description of
the “feature set” of the product.  On the information side, scope takes
the form of *content requirements*: a description of the various
elements that will be required.  Chapter 4 will cover the scope
elements.


