2.4.3 The Structure Plane
-------------------------

The scope is given structure on the functionality side through
*interaction design*, in which we define how the system behaves in
response to the user.  For information resources, the structure is the
*information architecture*: the arrangement of content elements to
facilitate human understanding.  You’ll find more details on these in
Chapter 5.


