2.4.5 The Surface Plane
-----------------------

Finally we have the surface.  Regardless of whether we are dealing with
a functionality-oriented product or an information resource, our concern
here is the same: the *sensory experience* created by the finished
product.  It’s trickier than it sounds; you can find out all about it in
Chapter 7.


